    <note>Gao(1) Ruona [911] His ancestors were Bohai jun Gao(1). He was noted for a synthesis of Guanzi, Han Feizi and Confucianism. Father-in-law of Zhang(1) Mian's [262] nephew, Yi(3) [3148]. His wife was a Taiyuan Wang and probably a descendant of Wang(2) Quanbin [11689], his great grandfather's brother-in-law. XCB, 174.15a; Wen Yanbo, WJ, 12.3a-9b; Song Qi, WJ, 60.1a-6b. CBD, 3, 1758.</note>
